### Test Borrow Records Search API with single 'q' parameter

### 1. Get borrow records by status with search (tìm kiếm cả tên sách và tên người dùng)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/borrow-records/status/borrowed?page=1&limit=10&q=Harry
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get borrow records by status with search (tìm kiếm theo tên người dùng)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/borrow-records/status/borrowed?page=1&limit=10&q=Nguyễn
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get borrow records by status with search (tìm kiếm theo tên sách)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/borrow-records/status/borrowed?page=1&limit=10&q=Potter
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get borrow records by status without search (original behavior)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/borrow-records/status/borrowed?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get borrow records by reader with search (tìm kiếm cả tên sách và tên người dùng)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/borrow-records/reader/{{readerId}}?page=1&limit=10&q=Harry
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get borrow records by reader with search (tìm kiếm theo tên sách)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/borrow-records/reader/{{readerId}}?page=1&limit=10&q=Potter
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get borrow records by reader with search (tìm kiếm theo tên người dùng)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/borrow-records/reader/{{readerId}}?page=1&limit=10&q=Nguyễn
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get borrow records by reader without search (original behavior)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/borrow-records/reader/{{readerId}}?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
